## Step 2: Configure the Agent

Use the IP address from the Serial Monitor output. The format is `id:host:port:tcp`.

<Tabs>
<TabItem label="Claude Desktop">
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "mcpu": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["mcpu-client"],
      "env": {
        "DEVICES": "mydevice:192.168.1.42:3000:tcp"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

